                            <comment id="94517" author="adilger" created="Fri, 19 Sep 2014 17:13:20 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Should be fixed for 2.4 with Oleg&apos;s patch from &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5525&quot; title=&quot;ASSERTION( new_lock-&amp;gt;l_readers + new_lock-&amp;gt;l_writers == 0 ) failed&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5525&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5525&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="94209" author="niu" created="Wed, 17 Sep 2014 02:35:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is caused by the flaw patch of &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4584&quot; title=&quot;Lock revocation process fails consistently&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-4584&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-4584&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, Oleg&apos;s correct fix from &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5525&quot; title=&quot;ASSERTION( new_lock-&amp;gt;l_readers + new_lock-&amp;gt;l_writers == 0 ) failed&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-5525&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-5525&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; ( &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/9488/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/9488/&lt;/a&gt;) should fix the problem.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
